index 2f7d17a8..72a93aae 100644
--- a/x-pack/plugin/sql/src/test/java/org/elasticsearch/xpack/sql/expression/function/scalar/datetime/DateFormatRandomDatasetGenerator.java
+++ b/x-pack/plugin/sql/src/test/java/org/elasticsearch/xpack/sql/expression/function/scalar/datetime/DateFormatRandomDatasetGenerator.java
@@ -88,7 +88,10 @@ public class DateFormatRandomDatasetGenerator {
     }
 
     private static LocalDateTime randomizedTimestamp() {
-        int year = RandomNumbers.randomIntBetween(RANDOM, 1000, 9999);
+        // Use a more reasonable year range to avoid issues with very early timestamps.
+        // Years 1900-2100 provide a good range while avoiding leap year calculation
+        // issues and time zone problems with dates too close to year 1000.
+        int year = RandomNumbers.randomIntBetween(RANDOM, 1900, 2100);
         int month = RandomNumbers.randomIntBetween(RANDOM, 1, 12);
         int dayOfMonth = RandomNumbers.randomIntBetween(RANDOM, 1, LocalDate.of(year, month, 1).lengthOfMonth());
         int hour = RandomNumbers.randomIntBetween(RANDOM, 0, 23);
